Cash flow Process¶

This is based on the principles of Zero-Sum

Barclaycard -> user. Set limit to Budget [500]... This amount is debited from Barclays .

  • Whatever is left, send to AMEX. Card.

Barclays -> No bills goes from here... Ideally if yes, Increase users monthly cash burn.

Monzo -> Set budget for cash burn. 1600 -> User salary goes to Barclays.. add that value to Cash burn. -> Whatever is left: Send to pot, or just write the number or manually do the transfer. -> Recurring Bills come from here.

Amex <- Do nothing, counts as Barclaycard surplus.!

If values are being recorded, every quarter, do the bank transfer. -> Monzo to pot. [Record the monthly expenses] -> Barclays to Amex. [Record the monthly expenses]
